entry.title: New release for Rybbit: Rybbit Initial Release
New release for Rybbit: v0.1.1
entry.content:
What's Changed

  • New env by @goldflag in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/122
  • Updated public-site documentation by @Thejus-Paul in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/123
  • Fix realtime page by @POLIROID in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/124
  • Enhance setup and configuration for self-hosting by @goldflag in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/125
  • add Quark browser logo by @POLIROID in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/126
  • add MIUI Browser logo by @POLIROID in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/127
  • fix ports by @goldflag in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/130

New Contributors

  • @Thejus-Paul made their first contribution in https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/pull/123

Full Changelog: https://github.com/rybbit-io/rybbit/compare/v0.1.0...v0.1.1
